title: The Frankenstein Chronicles S01E01 PDTV.x264-TVC mp4
description:
Set in Georgian London in 1827, The Frankenstein Chronicles incorporates elements from the investigative and horror genres with an extraordinary hero at its centre, Inspector John Marlott, played by multi-awarding winning leading actor Sean Bean, who is recruited by Sir Robert Peel to assist the investigation of a series of crimes, which may have been committed by a scientist intent on re-animating the dead.




The Frankenstein Chronicles - Series 1, Episode 1


A World Without God

When the police arrest a gang of opium smugglers on the banks of the Thames, Inspector John Marlott makes a shocking discovery in the form of the body of a dead child washed up on the shore. He is ordered by Home Secretary Sir Robert Peel to lead the investigation, however details must remain confidential.



Original Air Date: 11-Nov-2015
